msgid "New-ClusterAffinityRule"
msgstr "New-ClusterAffinityRule"

msgid "# New-ClusterAffinityRule"
msgstr "# 新集群亲和性规则"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid "Creates new affinity rules."
msgstr "创建新的亲和性规则。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"This cmdlet allows the creation of new affinity rules for a cluster, which can be used to control\n"
"whether certain roles (that is, virtual machines, resource groups, and so on) should run on the\n"
"same node. For more information, see\n"
"[Cluster affinity](/windows-server/failover-clustering/cluster-affinity)."
msgstr ""
"此 cmdlet 允许为集群创建新的亲和性规则，这些规则可用于控制某些角色（例如虚拟机、资源组等）是否应在同一节点上运行。有关更多信息，请参阅 "
"[集群亲和性](/windows-server/failover-clustering/cluster-affinity)。"

msgid ""
"The available rule types are: the same fault domain, different fault domain, same node, and\n"
"different node."
msgstr "可用的规则类型包括：相同的故障域、不同的故障域、相同的节点以及不同的节点。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1 - Create a new affinity rule"
msgstr "### 示例 1 - 创建一个新的亲和性规则"

msgid ""
"This command creates a new affinity rule for `Cluster1` to ensure resources stay within the same\n"
"fault domain."
msgstr "此命令为 `Cluster1` 创建一条新的亲和性规则，以确保资源始终位于同一个故障域内。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet as a background job. Use this parameter to run commands that take a long time to\n"
"complete."
msgstr "以后台作业的形式运行该 cmdlet。使用此参数来执行需要较长时间才能完成的命令。"

msgid ""
"The cmdlet immediately returns an object that represents the job and then displays the command\n"
"prompt. You can continue to work in the session while the job completes. To manage the job, use the\n"
"`*-Job` cmdlets. To get the job results, use the\n"
"[Receive-Job](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113372) cmdlet."
msgstr ""
"该cmdlet会立即返回一个表示该作业的对象，然后显示命令提示符。在作业完成之前，您可以继续在该会话中工作。要管理作业，请使用`*-Job`系列cmdlets；要获取作业结果，请使用[Receive-"
"Job](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113372) cmdlet。"

msgid ""
"For more information about PowerShell background jobs, see\n"
"[about_Jobs](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113251)."
msgstr ""
"有关 PowerShell 后台作业的更多信息，请参阅 "
"[关于作业](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113251)。"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet in a remote session or on a remote computer. Enter a computer name or a session\n"
"object, such as the output of a [New-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967)\n"
"or [Get-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966) cmdlet. The default is the\n"
"current session on the local computer."
msgstr ""
"在远程会话或远程计算机上运行该cmdlet。请输入计算机名称或会话对象（例如[New-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967)或[Get-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966) "
"cmdlet的输出结果）。默认值是本地计算机上的当前会话。"

msgid "The name of the rule to create."
msgstr "要创建的规则的名字。"

msgid ""
"The affinity type for the new rule. The valid values for this parameter are:"
msgstr "新规则的亲和类型（affinity type）。该参数的有效取值为："

msgid ""
"Specifies the maximum number of concurrent operations that can be established to run the cmdlet. If\n"
"this parameter is omitted or a value of `0` is entered, then PowerShell calculates an optimum\n"
"throttle limit for the cmdlet based on the number of CIM cmdlets that are running on the computer.\n"
"The throttle limit applies only to the current cmdlet, not to the session or to the computer."
msgstr ""
"指定可以同时执行的操作的最大数量。如果省略此参数或输入值 `0`，PowerShell 会根据计算机上正在运行的 CIM cmdlet 数量来计算该 "
"cmdlet 的最佳限制值。该限制仅适用于当前正在执行的 cmdlet，而不适用于整个会话或计算机本身。"

